stories.text:
Despite clearly that the items are available, I'm constantly getting "You cannot buy this item because it's out of stock" warning after I clicked the "place order" button.

The error page simply states that the item is out of stock but doesn't bother to tell me which one is out of stock. I tried a few times but the purchase couldn't go through. Sometime it shows the error page after I clicked the "check out" button as well.

I guess this is related to the issues Amazon experienced earlier this week?
